* {{a|US}} {{IPA|en|/ˈzɑtɑɹ/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# A particular [[herb]], similar in flavor to [[thyme]] or [[oregano]], used in [[Arab]] and [[Israeli]] [[cuisine]], made from various [[Middle Eastern]] [[herb]]s.
# A [[Middle Eastern]] [[seasoning]], having the herb as the main ingredient, with [[sumac]] (or other tart-flavored equivalent) and [[sesame]] seeds.

